title: Sundance filmfestival byter stad
description: Sundance filmfestival flyttar från Park City i Utah till Boulder i Colorado 2027. Festivalarrangörerna säger att man efter 40 år har vuxit ur staden Park City som saknar både tillräckliga biografer och bostäder för att kunna husera USA:s största filmfestival. Det som i dag kallas Sundancefestivalen grundades av bland andra skådespelaren och regissören Robert Redford och arrangerades första gången 1978 i Salt Lake City under namnet Utah/US film festival. Sedan 1981 har festivalen hållits i Park City och från 1984 med namnet Sundance.
title_translated: Sundance Film Festival changes city
description_translated: Sundance Film Festival moves from Park City in Utah to Boulder in Colorado 2027. The festival organizers say that after 40 years they have grown out of the city of Park City which lacks both sufficient cinemas and housing to be able to house the US's largest film festival. What is today called the Sundance Festival was founded by, among others, the actor and director Robert Redford and was first arranged in 1978 in Salt Lake City under the name Utah/US Film Festival. Since 1981, the festival has been held in Park City and from 1984 called Sundance.

I bilen hittar vi även ett föremål som gör att patrullen väljer att spärra av. Bombskyddet ska komma till platsen, säger Patric Fors, presstalesperson. Flygplanet försvann över Vinddalsvatnet vid Bjørnafjorden i tisdags eftermiddag efter att ha rapporterat om problem. En av de omkomna hittades i planet och den andra utanför. Norway's defense force, which helped with the search in the water, should try to salvage the bodies. The aircraft disappeared over the Winddalsvatnet at Bjørnafjord on Tuesday afternoon after reporting problems. One of the dead were found in the plane and the other outside. These are two men, 74 and 61 years old, where the older man was an instructor.

title: Angela Gui om gripandet av Medin: ”Inte en till”

Dottern till den i Kina fängslade Gui Minhai hoppas nu att det ska bli annorlunda för journalisten Joakim Medin, som sitter inlåst i Turkiet. ”Inte en till”. Det var en av Angela Guis första tankar när hon såg nyheten att Joakim Medin gripits i Turkiet i slutet av mars, skriver hon. Angela Guis far, den svensk-kinesiske förläggaren Gui Minhai, har – med undantag för kortare perioder – suttit i kinesiskt fängelse sedan 2015.
title_translated: Angela Gui about the arrest of Medin: "Not one to"
description_translated: The Ministry of Foreign Affairs has not been in a hurry and often acted too late when it comes to Swedes imprisoned in authoritarian regimes, writes Angela Gui in Expressen. The daughter of the Gui Minhai imprisoned in China now hopes that it will be different for journalist Joakim Medin, who is locked in Turkey. "Not another". It was one of Angela Gui's first thoughts when she saw the news that Joakim Medin was arrested in Turkey at the end of March, she writes. Angela Gui's father, the Swedish-Chinese publisher Gui Minhai, has-with the exception of shorter periods-been in Chinese prison since 2015.

title: Flicka död i fågelinfluensa i Mexiko
description: En treårig flicka i Mexiko har avlidit i fågelinfluensa, meddelar landets hälsomyndigheter. Flickan, hemmahörande i den nordliga delstaten Coahuila, var Mexikos första bekräftade fall av fågelinfluensa, meddelades det i helgen. Hon avled till en följd av organsvikt. Det är oklart exakt hur flickan smittades och det har heller inte upptäckts något mer misstänkt fall, enligt myndigheterna. Fågelinfluensan av typen H5N1 har spridits bland djur och en del människor i grannlandet USA. Under det senaste året har 70 fall konstaterats bland människor enligt Världshälsoorganisationen.
title_translated: Girl dead in bird flu in Mexico
description_translated: A three -year -old girl in Mexico has died in bird flu, the country's health authorities announce. The girl, a resident of the northern state of Coahuila, was Mexico's first confirmed case of bird flu, it was announced this weekend. She died as a result of organ failure. It is unclear exactly how the girl was infected and no more suspicious case has been discovered, according to the authorities. The bird flu of the type H5N1 has spread among animals and some people in neighboring the United States. During the past year, 70 cases have been found among people according to the World Health Organization.

title: Sveriges största fond har tappat mest
description: De senaste två månaderna har 21 miljarder kronor strömmat ut de svenska teknikfonderna, vilket har lätt till att nettoflödet för de senaste tre åren nu är negativt.Mars var den absolut sämsta månaden någonsin sett till utflöde. Försäljningen av teknikfonder slog då alla tidigare rekord, och svenska sparare sålde för hela 13 miljarder kronor. Det överträffade med råge utflödet på 8,4 miljarder i februari, rapporterar Morningstar.Populär teknikfond tappar mestMed ett förvaltat kapital på 173 miljarder är Swedbank Robur Technology Sveriges största fond. Men också den teknikfond som spararna sålde mest av förra månaden. Hela 8,5 miljarder kronor togs ut från fonden. Och det efter ett utflöde på 7 miljarder i februari. Fonden, som i år dessutom ligger på minus 30%, har därmed haft ett nettoutflöde av sparkapital på över 15 miljarder kronor under de senaste två månaderna.De svenska teknikfonderna har en stor exponering mot amerikanska bolag, vilka har pressats i börsturbulensen, och kan vara en orsaken till flykten.Även USA-fonderna såldes av i mars. Utflödet var över 12 miljarder kronor. Det är det största nettoutflödet på över två år, och slog det tidigare rekordet från mars 2020. Då orsakade coronapandemin stora rörelser.Bland de mest sålda fonderna i mars fanns Handelsbanken USA Index Criteria, där spararna tog ut 5 miljarder, följt av Handelsbanken Långränta. Spararna agerade även i Avanza Global och tog ut drygt 4,1 miljarder. Handelsbanken Företagsobligation Investment Grade hade i sin tur ett utflöde på 3,3 miljarder.Europa och Sverige vinnareSamtidigt fortsatte inflödet i anda fonder. Europafonder fick ta emot nästan 13 miljarder kronor, vilket var mer än dubbelt så mycket som det tidigare rekordet.Men svenska sparare fortsatte också att köpa Sverigefonder i mars. Men inflödet var långt ifrån rekordnivån i februari då nästan 24 miljarder placerades i kategorin. Nettoinflödet i Sverigefonder stannade på 5 miljarder i mars.Men börsoron till trots så fortsatte globalfonder att vara populära bland svenska sparare. Och det trots att dessa fonder ofta ligger mellan 70 och 90 % i amerikanska papper.Förmodligen beroende på att dessa fonder ägs av många sparare som fortsatt att månadsspara, enligt Morningstar.Handelsbanken Selection Global Equities och Handelsbanken Developed Markets Index Criteria var några av de mest köpa globalfonderna i mars.

Mars were by far the worst month ever in terms of outflow. The sale of technology funds then broke all previous records, and Swedish savers sold for a full SEK 13 billion. It exceeded with rye outflow of SEK 8.4 billion in February, reports Morningstar. A total of SEK 8.5 billion was withdrawn from the fund. And that after an outflow of SEK 7 billion in February. The fund, which this year is also minus 30%, has thus had a net outflow of savings capital of more than SEK 15 billion over the past two months. The Swedish technology funds have a great exposure to US companies, which have been pressed in the stock exchange turbulence, and may be a cause of the escape. The outflow was over SEK 12 billion. It is the largest net outflow for over two years, and broke the previous record from March 2020. Then the Coronapandemia caused large movements. Among the best -selling funds in March, the USA Index was made by the US index, where savers took out 5 billion, followed by Handelsbanken long -term. The savers also acted in Avanza Global and took out just over 4.1 billion. European funds received almost SEK 13 billion, which was more than twice as much as the previous record. But Swedish savers also continued to buy Swedish funds in March. But the inflow was far from the record level in February when almost 24 billion was placed in the category. The net inflow in Swedish funds stayed at SEK 5 billion in March. But despite the stock market turmoil, global funds continued to be popular with Swedish savers. And that despite the fact that these funds are often between 70 and 90 % in American paper. title: Kommunal varslar om strejk på Liseberg

Bakgrunden är att förhandlingarna om nytt avtal har strandat sedan arbetsgivarorganisationen Visita sagt nej till kravet att deltidsanställda ska få samma övertidsersättning som fastanställda. Strejken inleds morgonen den 26 april om parterna inte kan enas. Liseberg öppnar för säsongen den 17 april.
title_translated: Municipal warns of strike at Liseberg
description_translated: The trade union Municipal warns of strike at the Liseberg amusement park in Gothenburg, according to a press release. The reason is that the negotiations on a new agreement have been stranded since the employer organization Visita said no to the requirement that part -time employees should receive the same overtime compensation as permanent employees. The strike begins in the morning of April 26 if the parties cannot agree. Liseberg opens for the season on April 17.

title: Puerto Rico utan ström inför påsken
description: Det råder strömavbrott på Puerto Rico, meddelar energibolaget Luma Energy. Hela ön saknar ström, säger Hugo Sorrentini, talesperson för bolaget som levererar el till 1,4 miljoner kunder. Avbrottet drabbar den till stora delar katolska befolkningen på det självstyrande amerikanska territoriet mitt under förberedelserna inför påskhelgen. Liknande avbrott har skett tidigare på ön, bland annat på nyårsafton senast. Vad som orsakat strömavbrottet är oklart, men felsökning pågår, meddelar myndigheterna.
title_translated: Puerto Rico without power before Easter
description_translated: There is a power outage at Puerto Rico, the energy company Luma Energy announces. The entire island lacks power, says Hugo Sorrentini, spokesperson for the company who supplies electricity to 1.4 million customers. The interruption affects the largely Catholic population on the autonomous American territory in the midst of preparations for the Easter weekend. Similar interruptions have occurred earlier on the island, including on New Year's Eve. What caused the power outage is unclear, but troubleshooting is ongoing, the authorities announce.
